title: RB Rankings: 11-20 + Player Debates, Hard Knocks - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/10
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, debates continue as we dive into more running back rankings! Which mid-round running backs have the most upside? Is Ezekiel Elliott being undervalued? Will Javonte Williams be a major fantasy football breakout? Plus, early reactions to Hard Knocks! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 10th, 2022.
